'''CCleaner''' (formerly '''Crap Cleaner''') is a [[freeware]] utility used to optimize a user's computer and clean its registry. It is developed by [[Piriform (company)|Piriform]] and is designed for [[Microsoft Windows]]. CCleaner is offered free to anyone, though Piriform accepts donations for the program. CCleaner is available in 35 different languages, with more planned to be added. CCleaner has had over 250 million downloads.{{fact}}
